06/01/2003
BELGRADE, Yugoslavia -- The commission on the new Yugoslav Constitution will meet Monday (6 January), trying to reach final agreement on the law on enacting the charter.
Commission co-chairman Dragoljub Micunovic says he hopes the draft legislation will be finalised by the end of the week.
The final draft of the charter itself has been approved and signed.
(Tanjug - 06/01/03;
B92 - 05/01/03)
